    <div class="ml-40 mr-20">
      <h2>Building meaningful products since 2020</h2>
      <div class={styles.description}>
        <span>I am an electronic engineer who decided to change the direction of his career to focus on software development. In the last 4 years, I’ve worked as a full-stack developer, using  technologies like React JS, Vue JS, Vuetify, Tailwind CSS, Next JS, React Native, Flutter, NestJS, AWS CDK, mongodb, among others. I'm passionate about learning new things and am always looking for opportunities to improve my skills and stay up to date with the latest trends in software development.
